## Project Structure

```
src/app/            — pages and routes
src/components/     — UI components
src/lib/            — shared utilities, DB client
src/server/         — server-only logic (API routes, services)
prisma/             — database schema and migrations
```

## Code Conventions

### Frontend
- React functional components with TypeScript
- Colocate component, styles, and tests
- Use server components by default (Next.js)

### Backend
- Validate all request input with zod
- Return consistent response shapes: `{ data }` or `{ error }`
- Database queries in service layer, not in route handlers

### Database
- Every schema change requires a migration
- Never edit generated migration files

